@node QUARU "Quarum Trench Gnomes"

@{b}Quarum Trench Gnomes@{ub}

  Will only affect the land as long as it is producing white mana.  If the
    land type is changed to something else, the effect will continue if the
    new land type also makes white mana, but will do nothing if the land does
    not produce white mana.  Note that the effect is not removed, however, and
    it will resume as soon as the land qualifies for being affected again.
    [Aahz 11/08/96]

 @{" Card Information " link LG_RED.guide/QUARU}

@endnode
@node QLICI "Quickening Licid"

@{b}Quickening Licid@{ub}

+ As errata, change "instead of a creature" to "instead of any other type of
    permanent". [WotC Rules Team 12/18/97] [Duelist Magazine #22, Page 27]

 @{" Card Information " link TP_WHITE.guide/QUICK}

@endnode
@node QUIRI "Quirion Ranger"

@{b}Quirion Ranger@{ub}

  It can target an untapped creature. [D'Angelo 06/04/97]

 @{" Card Information          " link VI_GREEN.guide/QUIRA}

@endnode
